结好本世纪尾开好下世纪头? --访中国道教协会会长闵智亭</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td height="10"> </td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="right" class="text7">张敏</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td height="10"> </td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
